  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a pilot study is to test a wireless, skin-sensor device against current technology
      in the NICU to monitor vitals
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a single center, prospective, observational study that will recruit subjects from
      Lurie Children's Hospital to test a new wireless vitals monitor against the current vitals
      monitors used in the NICU. Patients will be neonates in different age brackets.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
